HEADWORD: Aslope
<hw>A*slope"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>adv. & a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>a-</ets> + <ets>slope</ets>.]</ety> <def>Slopingly; aslant;
